lem in the history of humanity. Fossil fuels are just too good for business=
=2E&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64,=20=
64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height=
: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">This is why I said that the climate crisis is =
