tion: underline;">environmentalists, economics, slowing energy demand, and =
disasters</a><span> &#8211; slowed new installs to a trickle. Germany even =
shut down its nuclear plants and replaced them with coal. Fortunately, at t=
he COP28 climate summit, the United States led a group of nations in </span=
><a href=3D"https://substack.com/redirect/7fb5e38f-7194-47ba-b804-1b53bcd87=
