ar-term. At the same time, government programs like the Department of Energ=
y and ARPA-E and climate-focused investors like Bill Gates&#8217; Breakthro=
ugh Energy and Lowercarbon Capital, have begun to pour significant dollars =
into private companies in the space.&#160;</p><div class=3D"captioned-image=
