<p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; mar=
gin: 0 0 20px 0;"><strong>Without the climate crisis, private fusion compan=
ies may not have gotten the talent or funding they needed to achieve fusion=
; now, it&#8217;s just a matter of who and when.</strong><span>&#160;</span=
></p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px=
; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>We haven&#8217;t defeated the boss yet. There =
is a gigaton of work left to be done to avoid warming the planet by more th=
