9-a7d6-0eb563be3e0f?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8=
-6m8ExkRNpU" rel style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); text-decoration: underlin=
e;">more besides</a><span>, to pull CO2 from the atmosphere.&#160;</span></=
p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; m=
argin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>If anything, humanity needs to put even </span><e=
m>more </em><span>effort into the energy transition. If the Climate Crisis =
