4, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">If we =
get this right, our kids will live in a world that&#8217;s more abundant an=
d more ethical than the one we inhabit today. They&#8217;ll look back at 20=
23 the same way we look back at 1712: wouldn&#8217;t want to live there, bu=
t thankful for the contributions of the people who did.&#160;</p><p style=
=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0=
 20px 0;">Climate change is real. It&#8217;s our current Boss. Defeating it=
 will require deft gameplay from millions of people, governments, and busin=
esses.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-h=
eight: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">But it doesn&#8217;t spell inevitable doo=
m, either. Humans are incredibly adaptable, and against all odds, we&#8217;=
ve created exactly the right tools to defeat it and unlock the next level a=
t exactly the right time.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font=
-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Having kids isn&#8217;=
t the problem; it&#8217;s the solution. It&#8217;s exactly because people w=
ho lived in much worse conditions than we do decided to have kids that we h=
ave the ultimate weapon in this game: human creativity.&#160;</p><p style=
=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0=
 20px 0;">Whatever challenges await on the next level, we&#8217;ll need all=
 the kids we can get to solve them.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64,=
 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>So don=
&#8217;t listen to the doom and gloom. It&#8217;s counterproductive, depres=
sing, and evil. It prioritizes clicks over your happiness and uses </span><=
a href=3D"https://substack.com/redirect/83450b59-295f-44ef-8e5e-9e3d68af163=
b?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU" rel s=
tyle=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); text-decoration: underline;">fear to sell a=
ds</a><span>. The people pretending to be ethical by being pessimistic are =
not the good guys; they&#8217;re villains in this game. </span></p><p style=
=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0=
 20px 0;">But villains can be useful, too. They&#8217;re part of the game. =
If that fear has motivated some of our best people to join the fight to bea=
t the boss and unlock the next level, humanity is better off for it. </p><p=
 style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margi=
n: 0 0 20px 0;">Just don&#8217;t let it depress you into hopeless inaction,=
 right when things are about to get really good. Don&#8217;t let it stop yo=
u from bringing kids into this world. </p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64=
); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">If we&#8217;re =
lucky, we might be alive to experience some of the wonders of this next lev=
el. I certainly hope to be.&#160;</p><div class=3D"captioned-image-containe=
